After I had an IUD in February 2018. We waited for a while and when we tried again to realise naturally conceiving was becoming a challenge. He patiently listens to us, friendly talkative and can be tuff at times if you don't follow his advice rightfully. Glad to be treated by a doctor who is highly efficient and passionate about his work. After consultation and assessment for few months, he advised laproscopic surgery which truly made an impact and I conceived in just a couple of months. Truly grateful to him and his amazing team for giving ray of hope again. I'm counting weeks, maybe days, soon to be mom again:-) :-) 

Many thanks to Dr. Sunil Eshwar and his team: Dr. Shivani Chandan, Dr. Smriti Nayak and Mrs. Naseemus Saher (Department Co-ordinator).
